column2: SELECT   g.gamaID,   g.RA AS g_ra,   g.DEC AS g_dec,   g.lmass,   g.lmass_err,   g.lmtoa,   g.lmtoa_err,   g.lage,   g.lage_err,   g.metal,   g.metal_err,   p.objID,   p.modelFlux_u AS F_u,   p.modelFlux_g AS F_g,   p.modelFlux_r AS F_r,   p.modelFlux_i AS F_i,   p.modelFlux_z as F_z,   p.modelFluxIvar_u AS E_u,   p.modelFluxIvar_g AS E_g,   p.modelFluxIvar_r AS E_r,   p.modelFluxIvar_i AS E_i,   p.modelFluxIvar_z AS E_z,   g.z_gama AS z_spec INTO MyDB.sdss1#_gamagals FROM MyDB.gamagals AS g   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(g.RA, g.DEC, #) AS near   INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary AS p ON p.objID=near.objID   INNER JOIN Galaxy AS g ON g.objID=p.objID
